1
00:00:00,005 --> 00:00:03,950
_

2
00:00:04,505 --> 00:00:06,338
(man) The Alamo's fallen!

3
00:00:06,440 --> 00:00:08,774
Santa Anna has taken the Alamo!

4
00:00:08,859 --> 00:00:14,947
♪ ♪

5
00:00:15,032 --> 00:00:17,649
Santa Anna took no prisoners.

6
00:00:17,752 --> 00:00:21,620
Sam, what would your personal compunctions

7
00:00:21,706 --> 00:00:23,372
lead you to do?

8
00:00:23,457 --> 00:00:26,959
Let Santa Anna get drunk on
an abundance of confidence,

9
00:00:27,044 --> 00:00:30,462
and then we attack with a vengeance.

10
00:00:30,548 --> 00:00:32,381
Sergeant Knowles?

11
00:00:32,466 --> 00:00:33,716
What the hell?

12
00:00:33,801 --> 00:00:35,768
Last we heard, youse was deserting.

13
00:00:35,793 --> 00:00:36,781
Now, just... easy.

14
00:00:36,823 --> 00:00:40,108
General Houston wants us
to track down Santa Anna.

15
00:00:40,195 --> 00:00:43,279
Come here. [crying]

16
00:00:43,345 --> 00:00:45,262
As long as you don't get,

17
00:00:45,347 --> 00:00:48,899
you and your men are
gonna be overrun and die.

18
00:00:49,018 --> 00:00:52,069
I've ordered Colonel Fannin
to retreat from Goliad.

19
00:00:52,187 --> 00:00:54,988
This is the very kind of deliberation

20
00:00:55,074 --> 00:00:58,241
that lost the lives of our compatriots

21
00:00:58,266 --> 00:00:59,482
at the Alamo!

22
00:01:03,198 --> 00:01:06,116
[dramatic music]

23
00:01:06,201 --> 00:01:14,207
♪ ♪

24
00:01:50,295 --> 00:01:58,301
♪ ♪

25
00:02:20,779 --> 00:02:26,825
